  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/a9803a4c9039f30d33a59f1a3c87bf87.avif?t=1733968330\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this adventure game, you play as a student trapped in a cursed junior high school, trying to escape while defeating zombies.<br>The game world, presented in realistic images, gives players an immersive experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/3aa61c69c6b1806403eeda7673ef9ce6.avif?t=1733968330\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras_big/3aa61c69c6b1806403eeda7673ef9ce6.avif?t=1733968330 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><strong>[Features of this game]</strong> <br>Dimly lit hallways, eerie classrooms, and zombies that suddenly appear - the visuals of a liver test will scare you. <br>If you don't remember the path you once took, you may get lost or encounter zombies. <br>Players choose their actions from three options: go forward, go back, or run away. <br>Zombies appear suddenly and unexpectedly, but players can escape by exterminating them without panicking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/97a177857561279ebac76ee3c7814a17.avif?t=1733968330\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras_big/97a177857561279ebac76ee3c7814a17.avif?t=1733968330 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><strong>[Story]</strong> <br>Strange stories have spread about this junior high school. <br>It is rumored that at midnight, zombies in the form of women appear in the restrooms, <br>As time went by, it turned into a horror. <br>Do not play this game if you have a weak heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/1ddbbce32710090a6f7d9eab621fd312.avif?t=1733968330\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras_big/1ddbbce32710090a6f7d9eab621fd312.avif?t=1733968330 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><strong>[Play time]</strong> <br>About 10 to 45 minutes to complete the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/311f114d0f7ca9d28a0c001b3f9ae2f7.avif?t=1733968330\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras_big/311f114d0f7ca9d28a0c001b3f9ae2f7.avif?t=1733968330 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/a9803a4c9039f30d33a59f1a3c87bf87.avif?t=1733968330\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this adventure game, you play as a student trapped in a cursed junior high school, trying to escape while defeating zombies.<br>The game world, presented in realistic images, gives players an immersive experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/3aa61c69c6b1806403eeda7673ef9ce6.avif?t=1733968330\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras_big/3aa61c69c6b1806403eeda7673ef9ce6.avif?t=1733968330 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><strong>[Features of this game]</strong> <br>Dimly lit hallways, eerie classrooms, and zombies that suddenly appear - the visuals of a liver test will scare you. <br>If you don't remember the path you once took, you may get lost or encounter zombies. <br>Players choose their actions from three options: go forward, go back, or run away. <br>Zombies appear suddenly and unexpectedly, but players can escape by exterminating them without panicking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/97a177857561279ebac76ee3c7814a17.avif?t=1733968330\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras_big/97a177857561279ebac76ee3c7814a17.avif?t=1733968330 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><strong>[Story]</strong> <br>Strange stories have spread about this junior high school. <br>It is rumored that at midnight, zombies in the form of women appear in the restrooms, <br>As time went by, it turned into a horror. <br>Do not play this game if you have a weak heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/1ddbbce32710090a6f7d9eab621fd312.avif?t=1733968330\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras_big/1ddbbce32710090a6f7d9eab621fd312.avif?t=1733968330 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><strong>[Play time]</strong> <br>About 10 to 45 minutes to complete the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras/311f114d0f7ca9d28a0c001b3f9ae2f7.avif?t=1733968330\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925980/extras_big/311f114d0f7ca9d28a0c001b3f9ae2f7.avif?t=1733968330 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
